io.micronaut.context.env

Interface PropertySource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>, Ordered
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CommandLinePropertySource, EmptyPropertySource, EnvironmentPropertySource, MapPropertySource, SystemPropertiesPropertySource

    public interface PropertySource
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>, Ordered
    A PropertySource is a location to resolve property values from. The property keys are are available via the Iterable.iterator() method.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Graeme Rocher
